Others include a youth having a cell phone in addition to one provided by parents, or bruises or other injuries for which the teen doesn’t have a good explanation.

data.description: Modesto police and the nonprofit Without Permission produce a back-to-school video warning parents of the risks of human trafficking.
data.title: Is your teen at risk for human trafficking?
